    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进游3大福利礼包大放送</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >dalao1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >dalao2</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >dalao3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加官方QQ群：698482009，还有更多福利等你来领！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加时请备注：妖神记</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款您从未体验过的像素+卡牌+自走棋的策略爽游。开服就送和UR妖灵师聂离（超强肉盾）、叶紫芸（控制爆发）、肖凝儿（核心控制）和海量招募券，让您轻松打造属于自己的妖灵师阵容，闯荡整个世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/e4279688dc46a8210dc97d21044466db.avif?t=1735261303\" width=798 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★拒绝换皮！独创能量变身战斗玩法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款主打变身的自走棋你见过吗？在《妖神记之巅峰对决》中，玩家需要集中精力，关注战场情况，合理分配时空能量给不同的妖灵师，完成变身，击败强敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能量分配：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/063794bd852bb85b7735cfa1c64e6bfa.poster.avif?t=1735261303\" width=800 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/063794bd852bb85b7735cfa1c64e6bfa.webm?t=1735261303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/063794bd852bb85b7735cfa1c64e6bfa.mp4?t=1735261303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妖灵师变身：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/22d374ff5267e60d1a0587b11c1e855a.poster.avif?t=1735261303\" width=800 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/22d374ff5267e60d1a0587b11c1e855a.webm?t=1735261303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/22d374ff5267e60d1a0587b11c1e855a.mp4?t=1735261303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★成男熟女！硬核立绘传承九年国漫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年少的我们终会长大，而陪伴我们的角色也在成长！男角色眼神坚毅，似曾游历四方，闯荡天地，闯出一番好名声；女角色娴淑典雅，出淤泥而不染，濯清涟而不妖。成熟风的立绘，见证了国漫的成长，也见证了我们自己的成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/653aa7eee2d67b873a9c24a478c43d38.avif?t=1735261303\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras_big/653aa7eee2d67b873a9c24a478c43d38.avif?t=1735261303 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★闯关推图！开箱爆UR妖灵师欧气满满！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UR妖灵师不用抽也能获得！通过推主线关卡和黑魔森林，可以获得宝箱，而开宝箱可以爆出UR妖灵师，直接一键起飞！同时推更多的主线关卡，每小时通过离线挂机获得的角色养成资源就更多，让您在推关的同时轻松养成自己的妖灵师！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/a8dd1936c541b703c1188e27625e1560.avif?t=1735261303\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras_big/a8dd1936c541b703c1188e27625e1560.avif?t=1735261303 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★全新玩法！自由世界探索神器宝藏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《妖神记之巅峰对决》中，玩家可以化身为像素小人，在像素的世界中自由探寻～在这个世界中，有许许多多的奇怪宝藏，玩家可以一边讨伐怪物，一边探寻宝藏，进而提升妖灵师的能力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/93250ed5bd275f726365477c4351f8b0.poster.avif?t=1735261303\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/93250ed5bd275f726365477c4351f8b0.webm?t=1735261303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/93250ed5bd275f726365477c4351f8b0.mp4?t=1735261303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★海量福利！狂送自选备战云顶之巅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别人送抽奖，我们直接送UR妖灵师！上线不仅送UR妖灵师自选礼盒，同时还送UR妖灵师聂离、叶紫芸、肖凝儿，搭配赠送的海量招募券，让玩家轻松集齐核心妖灵师，享受不一样的阵容搭配，开启新的冒险旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras/c566cb35cb091e98d80332e6b1fc9d28.avif?t=1735261303\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241230/extras_big/c566cb35cb091e98d80332e6b1fc9d28.avif?t=1735261303 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强大的妖灵师们，快来下载《妖神记之巅峰对决》吧，我们都在云巅之上等着你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
